{"tid":528030,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[我是歌手冇人開？] 歌手2018 Jessie J 嚟中國屌打班支那歌手 :o)","createTime":"2018-01-13T10:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T09:29:00.000Z","uid":123522,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ffa9149de33d2cbeea008acd00711a33f4a51b","tid":528030,"uid":123522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T10:40:29.000Z","msg":"全片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LuRVffwKlNk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLuRVffwKlNk&d=tUDocn2BGiz%2BSbheuNsau9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=58d51dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LuRVffwKlNk</a><br />\n<br />\n其實到左第六年已經冇咩大歌手肯入來俾支那觀眾指指點點，好多傳左好耐嘅大明星全部都冇嚟到，但可能做左個名出嚟，反而呃到Jessie J咁大粒星嚟吸金加表演。但其實咁做反而更加衰，拉大左歌手嘅level差距，搞到比賽嚟都冇意思，根本就冇得鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常發揮嘅Jessie J都起馬贏十條街喇仆街，輸左攞唔到第一又一定比人話做馬，宜家變到好似冇咩意思，客客氣氣表演咁，何況今季啲人又唔係勁，真係冇咩火花同癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話有幾個Eason 張學友 張惠妹 姐倫 起馬都薛之謙 呢啲level先會有feel夠揪姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家最勁得汪峰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都廢事俾。有劇本還有劇本 ，有內定還有內定，但你起馬都寫份精采啲嘅劇本我睇下喇大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過冇得鬥還冇得鬥 但其實李聖杰 張韶涵 GAI爺 同埋果位不知名大叔 呢啲歌手嘅表演同技巧都真心唔錯，認真唱得幾好，但就唔似係競爭緊而係變左表演咁囉，Jessie J一出黎就知道唔係同一皮，搞到個氣氛唔緊張。<br />\n<br />\n同埋我幾中意個新人張天 佢把聲好沈同好powerful好有味道好有台風，條腳仲幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，香港人但ABC type，希望會唱廣東話歌同埋可以成長為第二個宇宙漿 Level <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4JwmymCkdpA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4JwmymCkdpA&d=tUDocn2BGiz%2BSbheuNsau9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d419a61f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4JwmymCkdpA</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左一集 我覺得呢一季歌手值 6/10 分 當比賽嚟睇就幾悶同冇咩意思 但當音樂表演節目嚟睇都還可以。同埋可以改名做《我是修音》因為一聽就知Tune左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但見到支那國咁多成本搞流行音樂 香港就連勁歌金曲都就黎要摺埋咁真係有啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真心希望香港會再有新一代好歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cd5a5b40d24b52e1f2243bb00d6e9dc21ff14f","tid":528030,"uid":12367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"唱多幾集就會因健康等等退出架啦"},{"pid":"bddce18b13687472dc318bac951007767f7fba6e","tid":528030,"uid":79577,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"Gai爺真心唔錯 台風不流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5931ab0d78de7b7aa08ce72b658e23421f14930c","tid":528030,"uid":79577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bddce18b13687472dc318bac951007767f7fba6e","tid":528030,"uid":79577,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:27:08.000Z","msg":"Gai爺真心唔錯 台風不流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:27:18.000Z","msg":"一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6673f87c75cd2e88169f8197f6a0dc0dd5490bb1","tid":528030,"uid":98507,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:15:15.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦薛之謙唱LIVE難聽到嘔喎<br />\n<br />\n仲有李聖傑近年越唱越衰 高音上唔到假音又虛 有時仲好似比人摙住個袋唔夠氣咁<br />\n<br />\n聽左第一集係GAI叫做好少少 其他都似有TUNE過音黎"},{"pid":"cce0e4d4e15aa0c450fa53bc4536b23ea5a5ead5","tid":528030,"uid":28456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:50:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m0L8E6SaTrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm0L8E6SaTrE&d=tUDocn2BGiz%2BSbheuNsau9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ffd6ddf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m0L8E6SaTrE</a><br />\nGai依首係成集亮點 改編得好正 中國風+hiphop+搖滾"},{"pid":"3a15e473fd1c3b1476274ab0f8696af2eb8fb064","tid":528030,"uid":84289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"Jessie J. 一出黎同其他人差幾班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db51c04b370e841dfdbe6e53213c4ac7d6e9cb46","tid":528030,"uid":111497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:04:29.000Z","msg":"好好奇汪峰把聲真係禁入咪?拉到個咪離天百丈遠...好記得佢之前好聲音..佢唱D ROCK野係完全無聲..比D樂器蓋晒..但佢都仲要拉禁遠.."},{"pid":"9345be13c83784fdd245fb2aaf9b0f89d5b9f317","tid":528030,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T19:33:25.000Z","msg":"Jessie J啲節奏真係聽到有啲唔耐煩"},{"pid":"b4e6c5d99f906fa011587e3aec25fb87276515fc","tid":528030,"uid":16881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T20:23:37.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩啦張天唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽果陣覺得佢勁嘈"},{"pid":"f6459e4f08f8c726505b3d4617d380e7d1a899d0","tid":528030,"uid":132156,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"Jessie J 去大陸登台仲唔係政治show?<br />\n有人想緩和中美關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00451accd43f926b8d9712db0ba5fe21c7690d7","tid":528030,"uid":2360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f6459e4f08f8c726505b3d4617d380e7d1a899d0","tid":528030,"uid":132156,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0